近排搵左英國個公務員體制望一望，其實人地公務員確係嘛嘛地，真係有心做public affairs既精英，一係入政府既management trainee program，捱到就比個deputy director既位你坐；再唔係就做policy adviosr。<br />
英國文職公務係得：Administrative assistant &gt; Administrative Officer &gt; Executive Officer &gt; Higher Executive Officer &gt; Senior Executive Officer &gt; Deputy Director &gt; Director &gt; ... &gt; Permanent Secretary。<br />
任你做到最高既ps，都係做緊內閣大臣既頭馬&hellip; &hellip;

